An interesting thing about applying group concept to GUI specs (like above)
    Rather than having some program processing and interpreting attributes
    The group concept turns that on its head; and attributes can be invoked to process and interpret themselves. Do not need to implement a program to deal with lots of different stuff.
    Program just has to deal with itself (and its input). Work gets mostly done by other little programs
